cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper proposes a resistive memory network for cognitive functionality, which is a topic related to neural networks and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves character recognition, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the proposed network has a hierarchical modular architecture, which is a topic related to systems and control (cs.SY).
